      {
        "id": 282986,
        "name": null,
        "username": "Peller",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/c2a13f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-17T20:14:39.919Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The accessibility does not only affect the users who need it, but all other users in two ways:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Better legibility is good for everyone, even if you can also read it with worse legibility.</li>\n<li>If you have any contacts, that need better accessibility and therefore use another messenger, you have to use that other messenger too, only to contact them.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Therefore accessibility (in this case: contrast) should be improved.</p>",
